{"tid":908991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死前力戰群狗及獵人 野鹿與12隻獵犬一同墜崖","createTime":"2018-11-20T04:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T08:48:02.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb22ab3a0714310d3c9ff2385c327af9b96f053b","tid":908991,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"西班牙一名獵人，日前命令大批獵犬，在懸崖邊圍捕一頭野鹿，過程中有人大聲警告「讓狗這麼做，很危險」，要求適可而止，但獵人沒有理會，結果混戰中，有12隻獵犬及野鹿先後墜崖。<br />\n  <br />\n西班牙動保政黨「反對虐待動物黨」（Partido Antitaurino contra el Maltrato Animal，PACMA）周日（18日）公布這段於卡塞雷斯省（Caceres）埃雷魯埃拉鎮（Herreruela）拍攝的影片。<br />\n <br />\n影片中，一批獵犬在崖邊攻擊一頭野鹿，因為地勢險要，很快就有兩隻獵犬跌落懸崖，隨後獵人來到崖邊，出手拉扯野鹿，並用刀刺向牠。期間有目擊者大叫：「快走開，狗要掉下去了」，但獵人沒有收手，最後因為野鹿奮力掙扎，多隻獵犬與野鹿均從崖上墜落，發出巨響。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙皇家狩獵聯盟（Real Federacion Espanola de Caza）指，墜崖的獵犬後來獲現場的專業人士搶救後，送往附近的動物醫院，但不清楚最後是否倖存。西班牙左翼「我們可以黨」（Podemos）黨魁伊格萊西亞斯．圖里翁（Pablo Iglesias Turrion）譴責批評，犯下這種暴行的人是罪犯份子，要求當局重懲。PACMA則指，狩獵活動本身相當殘酷，呼籲執政黨立法禁止獵人利用動物狩獵，但有支持狩獵的團體辯稱，這次只是個別事件，單純是「狗的天性及直覺」，導致慘劇發生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181120/1469505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181120%2F1469505&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e10516fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181120%2F1469505&h=3f472c45\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181120/1469505</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tg9nrQYM-JA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTg9nrQYM-JA&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=1b497f82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tg9nrQYM-JA</a><br />\n<br />\n好正"},{"pid":"197f3371d1159a4d3c5a83447624338b08388fee","tid":908991,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b527189140c128c57e4d91e02397ef71c36abcc3","tid":908991,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"197f3371d1159a4d3c5a83447624338b08388fee","tid":908991,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"人地真焦土"},{"pid":"bf97bcc78fab440ef19440f2063f702557af3856","tid":908991,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:26:47.000Z","msg":"屌 d狗跌完都仲跑到 幾撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bd1193743100032bf7800fafd54c38ff1ca918","tid":908991,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf97bcc78fab440ef19440f2063f702557af3856","tid":908991,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:26:47.000Z","msg":"屌 d狗跌完都仲跑到 幾撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"下面有野LONG住 , 只是好彩"},{"pid":"2e4e247b2297a4f2d6c6deda43fb5030f6d7686b","tid":908991,"uid":158806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"獵犬終須山上喪"},{"pid":"c8ef9d318453386cb1fba17f667e0d94ba522340","tid":908991,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"禁止利用動物狩獵，唔係禁止狩獵<br />\n呢個係乜嘢動物組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c501708d2323e28efcdf15bfcb80427ce5e5b4","tid":908991,"uid":182286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb9aef7d5d2629154966c122d982c02802535134","tid":908991,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c501708d2323e28efcdf15bfcb80427ce5e5b4","tid":908991,"uid":182286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018